{"id":610802,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2019/05/【立此存照】抵制还没达成一致-立马禁评/","date":"2019-05-20T17:17:35Z","modified":"2019-05-20T17:18:34Z","title":"【立此存照】“抵制”还没达成一致 立马“禁评”了？","content":"<p>5月20日，针对“谷歌暂停向华为提供服务”的<a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2019/05/%e5%be%b7%e5%9b%bd%e4%b9%8b%e5%a3%b0-google%e5%81%9c%e6%ad%a2%e4%b8%8e%e5%8d%8e%e4%b8%ba%e5%90%88%e4%bd%9c-%e8%bf%99%e4%ba%9bapps%e9%83%bd%e4%b8%8d%e8%83%bd%e7%94%a8/\">有关新闻</a>，新京报的新浪微博账号跟进了此事，报道了中国外交部对此的回应：</p>\n<blockquote><p>@新京报：在今天的外交部例行记者会上，发言人陆慷表示，中方注意到有关谷歌公司已经暂停对华为公司涉及软硬件转让业务并且暂停向华为提供有关服务的说法。中方将正式确认此事，并进一步积极关注事态进展。同时，中方支持中国企业拿起法律武器捍卫自己的正当权利。</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-610807\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/05/新京报3.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"450\" height=\"305\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/05/新京报3.jpg 739w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/05/新京报3-300x203.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 450px) 100vw, 450px\" /></p>\n<p><strong>相关阅读：</strong></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2011/03/%E5%A4%96%E4%BA%A4%E9%83%A8%EF%BC%9A%E5%A4%96%E5%9B%BD%E8%AE%B0%E8%80%85%E4%B8%8D%E8%A6%81%E6%8B%BF%E6%B3%95%E5%BE%8B%E5%BD%93%E6%8C%A1%E7%AE%AD%E7%89%8C/\">外交部姜瑜：外国记者不要拿法律当挡箭牌</a></p></blockquote>\n<p>然而有网友发现，该<a href=\"https://weibo.com/1644114654/Hv4Bphc6e\">微博</a>下很快聚集了大量的“高赞评论”，声明中国应“抵制谷歌”、“抵制安卓”、“支持国货”，并且评论数目持续增加。据悉，另一些网友也加入评论中，以“回复”方式表达不同意见。</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">（以下内容来自网友截图）</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-610808\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/05/D6-4B3EUcAAFbqW.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"912\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/05/D6-4B3EUcAAFbqW.jpg 657w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/05/D6-4B3EUcAAFbqW-164x300.jpg 164w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/05/D6-4B3EUcAAFbqW-561x1024.jpg 561w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /> <img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-610809\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/05/D6-4B3FUYAACz2r.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"919\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/05/D6-4B3FUYAACz2r.jpg 653w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/05/D6-4B3FUYAACz2r-163x300.jpg 163w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/05/D6-4B3FUYAACz2r-557x1024.jpg 557w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /> <img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-610810\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/05/D6-4B3GUwAAiFCK.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"912\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/05/D6-4B3GUwAAiFCK.jpg 657w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/05/D6-4B3GUwAAiFCK-164x300.jpg 164w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/05/D6-4B3GUwAAiFCK-561x1024.jpg 561w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /> <img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-610811\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/05/D6-4B3HUYAAxpjc.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"915\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/05/D6-4B3HUYAAxpjc.jpg 656w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/05/D6-4B3HUYAAxpjc-164x300.jpg 164w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/05/D6-4B3HUYAAxpjc-560x1024.jpg 560w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p>然而，在中国数字时代编辑于北京时间5月20日23点对新京报微博内容进行确认的时候，发现新京报已将相关内容全面<a href=\"https://weibo.com/1644114654/Hv4Bphc6e\">关闭了评论</a>。至于关闭评论的原因，可能于微博下的讨论超出“内容可控”有关。</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-610812\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/05/新京报4.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"715\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/05/新京报4.jpg 635w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/05/新京报4-231x300.jpg 231w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n","author":1004,"categories":[18271,18270,18269,27949],"tags":[32327,18448]}